>questions about my personal life were marked "voluntary but required"!)
>
>Here's the question: how do I take my keys back?

Worse, if the government gets a wiretap order, they can retroactively tap
everything you've EVER said with your Clipperphone.  If someone can explain
why this is acceptable, I'd like to hear it...
